ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>

[As mentioned above, this is the 1st imported case of MERS-CoV infection identified in the Netherlands. Details on this case are still pending, including age, location visited within Saudi Arabia, possible exposures in Saudi Arabia (healthcare contact, animal/camel contact, animal product contact, contact with known MERS-CoV infected individuals), and the purpose of the trip (worked in Saudi Arabia, visited family or friends). More information addressing the epidemiology of this case would be greatly appreciated.

For a map of the Netherlands, see http://healthmap.org/r/awDr. - Mod.MPP]

